Requirements:
=============

- make 3.81
- Fortran 2003 compiler: 
        gfortran 4.5
        ifort 11.1
- cfitsio 3.23
- FFTW3 3.2.2 (compiled with openMP enabled)
- wcslib 4.4.4
- python 2.6 (numpy, scipy, matplotlib)
- ipython
- PyFFTW3 0.2 with patches (https://launchpad.net/pyfftw)
- pyfits 2.3 (http://www.stsci.edu/resources/software_hardware/pyfits)

Recommended package:
====================
- kapteyn (http://www.astro.rug.nl/software/kapteyn/index.html)

